Vendored OpenTelemetry protobuf definitions — v1.3.2 stable
Source: https://github.com/open-telemetry/opentelemetry-proto (tag v1.3.2)

Files included (exact upstream content, byte-faithful):
  opentelemetry/proto/collector/trace/v1/trace_service.proto
  opentelemetry/proto/trace/v1/trace.proto
  opentelemetry/proto/common/v1/common.proto
  opentelemetry/proto/resource/v1/resource.proto

Import paths are preserved exactly as upstream so Grpc.Tools resolves them.
ProtoRoot in the .csproj points at this directory.

Do not hand-edit these files. If upgrading: replace with the new upstream content,
re-run dotnet build to regenerate the C# bindings, and verify the AOT publish is clean.
